{
  "text": "Low genetic diversity was found within B. columnaris in the Netherlands. Multi-locus genetic analysis revealed four distinct genotypes, possibly owing to the differences in the host or geographic origin of these parasites [CITATION_1] . However, a wider sampling of infected hosts from other geographical regions is warranted to reveal the true genetic diversity of these parasites.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "14257672"
